{"tid":2362443,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府取消農曆年宵市場","createTime":"2021-01-11T12:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T14:29:24.000Z","uid":291865,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1775a2c922630e4db908501419058b9ec143aa3a","tid":2362443,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:30:19.000Z","msg":"政府取消年宵　有花農建議以流動車方式賣花<br />\n<br />\n#港聞 政府取消農曆年宵市場，食環署約見花農商討其他方案，大部分出席的花農不接受到街市賣花。 (1/11/20:23) 全文"},{"pid":"c93e454cacd4f2bbeb47f4053799426a6b090733","tid":2362443,"uid":16676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:31:51.000Z","msg":"小販合法化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個拉車仔檔"},{"pid":"4ded15b3dd6409686b32c52cbc1f0a617a8440ec","tid":2362443,"uid":58630,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:32:05.000Z","msg":"流動車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點搞花truck"},{"pid":"31bd43d2187851ef86096bfa62347654ba673597","tid":2362443,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:33:47.000Z","msg":"當初年宵就係統一控制人流, 小販, 貪污, 衛生, 市容, 治安<br />\n各種新年問題"},{"pid":"809049e4222ef3eeaec86a84003bb6c660574366","tid":2362443,"uid":191474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:35:35.000Z","msg":"流動車？<br />\n2016新年 旺角既流動車最後變成點？"},{"pid":"67f60cec7196b5503800860feee58720f28bcb37","tid":2362443,"uid":228995,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:36:08.000Z","msg":"政府早前以防疫為由取消今年濕貨年宵，本地花農料蝕百萬元貨叫苦連天。食環署今（11日）下午邀請業界開會，惟會議開始後不夠句鐘，花農陸續離場。原料能在維園擺十多個檔位的「桃花大王」劉海濤怒斥，政府「空口講白話，全部呃人！」他又指署方不是如邀請開會時所說的收集意見，而是僅通知業界將僅有屋邨擺檔單一選擇，認為對方無意聽意見，「我唔係要五大訴求，我得一個訴求啫，開返年宵」。"},{"pid":"685c0fe8e7e95baebf2025d70adbfc8e91922d9c","tid":2362443,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:36:21.000Z","msg":"好啊"},{"pid":"ce54b60d3d81e1c7b91fb0b5672ff1efe6c0b024","tid":2362443,"uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"楊指，在場有人只望當局「回水」每個檔口8萬元，「有鬼用咩？水費都唔夠畀啦」。他續斥取消年宵，人流同樣會逼在花墟或署方期望的屋邨花市，「仆你個街，咁就唔會傳染咩？咪一樣」。他重申若署方無重啟維園年宵之意則無討論價值，故與會後半小時已離場。"},{"pid":"823c3c715d82cda15b6bd8bb8a0899c4263b62e5","tid":2362443,"uid":344701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:36:58.000Z","msg":"幾時取消埋返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 凍冰冰唔想落床<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94140fca8a8cfd9e26afa9aa5acbc2d3708fd43","tid":2362443,"uid":185492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:37:13.000Z","msg":"租美食車賣花啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e338d5490c1a84e87300d9b4e55d270a097293c2","tid":2362443,"uid":333796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:37:46.000Z","msg":"班新界佬，經常係政府嘅支持者，最好餓死佢哋"},{"pid":"96d9506eb257869057852807b113243d7594c64b","tid":2362443,"uid":129169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:38:31.000Z","msg":"政府「空口講白話，全部呃人！ <br />\n依家先知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑死"},{"pid":"9a2783620ecc102da09054f3b6ddb1856834401c","tid":2362443,"uid":185492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce54b60d3d81e1c7b91fb0b5672ff1efe6c0b024","tid":2362443,"uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"楊指，在場有人只望當局「回水」每個檔口8萬元，「有鬼用咩？水費都唔夠畀啦」。他續斥取消年宵，人流同樣會逼在花墟或署方期望的屋邨花市，「仆你個街，咁就唔會傳染咩？咪一樣」。他重申若署方無重啟維園年宵之意則無討論價值，故與會後半小時已離場。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"Show 已做完<br />\n你地自己顧自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb87e961c56af8936b6391ac272952df0a7d5376","tid":2362443,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim